Requirements
~~~~~~~~~~~~
ROX 2.1.0 or higher
ROX-Lib2 2.0.0 or higher
Pygtk 1.9.18 or better?
Python 2.3 or better


Instructions
~~~~~~~~~~~~
Drag the AppIcon to the Panel to run as an applet.
Left click to show the application menu.
Middle click to open the directory with your ROX applications in a filer window.
Middle click + drag to position the applet.
Right click for the options menu. From there you can:
    - open the directory with your ROX applications in a filer window.
    - request the applet to rebuild the application menu from disk.
    - view the program (version number, authors, website etc.)
    - open the option edit dialog to set the directory containing your ROX
      applications.
    - close the applet.

Email the authors for help :)
    Ken Hayber <ken@hayber.us>
    Christopher Arndt <chris@chrisarndt.de>

Written in Python, pygtk and ROX-Lib2.
